channel.title: Getting rid of nulls off of ::players [it laggs server]
channel.description:
it laggs the server.. when you look at ::players i see tons of nulls.. someone gave be a website on a file needed downloaded and imported in server to get rid of it.. but it brought up an error clicking on the link..
can someone show me step by step please i need your help,
Thanks,
Brandon [CEO RomeScape]

item.title: Getting rid of nulls off of ::players [it laggs server]
item.dc:creator: @sp3c sp3c
item.description:
@sp3c wrote:

Here’s what I did when someone tried crashing my server with nulls, I saw the same ip logging in over and over in my server screen, so I banned the ip, restarted my server, and it stopped. This might be a more advanced crasher that makes it less noticable, but mine thank goodness, wasn’t.
